hopobject.body: How long are you planning to stay here? kamagra hatsa Let's go back to my first semester at the University of Alabama, writes U.S. News blogger Steven Holbrook. It was the night before my first collegiate final exam – an introductory economics class, I think – and I was, frankly, not ready for it. So, being a typical arrogant freshman, I thought, "Oh, no problem. I'll just pull an all-nighter, ace the test and be playing NBA 2K11 by lunchtime. Piece of cake."
